## Check your understanding

1. **Why do prose instructions ("handle null input gracefully") produce inconsistent results across runs?** Prose is ambiguous -- "gracefully" could mean return `None`, return an empty string, raise a custom exception, log and skip, or any number of interpretations. Each time the model generates, it may pick a different interpretation.

